-- MOVES-Anna Hartropp joins Liberum Capital from Laird
-- 
-- Wed Aug 13, 2014 05:47AM EDT
-- None



Aug 13 (Reuters) - Investment bank Liberum Capital Ltd said it hired Anna Hartropp from technology company Laird Plc <LRD.L>.

Hartropp will focus on investment banking services for corporate clients, Liberum said in a statement. Before joining Liberum, Hartropp was director of investor relations and corporate communications at Laird.